HEADWORD: Amen-Ra
<hw>Amen-Ra</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The ancient Egyptian sun god;
supreme god of the universe in whom Amen and Ra were combined; the
principal deity during the Theban supremacy.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Amon-Ra</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>A mensa et thoro</ent>⟦br⟧
